pros:
good training opportunities with different aircraft types;
standard airline travel benefits;
there are opportunities for internal transfer within the same department or to a different department

cons:
bonding is required for training, and not consistent among staff; 
roster is 5 on 2 off with off days not fixed and often times 2 off days are apart (roster can also change any time without staff awareness in advance);
no confirmation for annual leave plan;
top quality international with local salary range;
